{"tid":1365170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花] 44部門逾200公務員促林鄭回應社會訴求  否則籌備工業行動跟市民同行","createTime":"2019-07-25T14:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T11:37:02.000Z","uid":259088,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e9bd27082d8aa80e1ac2811cdf53c1d7e6ae9bed","tid":1365170,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:27:05.000Z","msg":"有良知公職人員好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》修訂爭議未平息，上周日(21日)又有大批白衣人在元朗西鐵站暴打市民，造成至少45人受傷。繼多名行政主任(EO)、紀律部隊人員及其他政府部門相繼在網上討論區發表公開信，促特首林鄭月娥回應社會訴求後，來自44個決策局、部門及單位共235名政府人員今日(25日)亦向林鄭月娥發公開信，批評政府一直拒絕聆聽大眾聲音，違背服務市民的承諾，令公務員成為社會撕裂的幫兇，強烈要求政府回應社會訴求，否則「將籌備具體工業行動，謙卑地與廣大香港的市民同行」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2410671/%E3%80%90%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E3%80%9144%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80%E9%80%BE200%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E4%BF%83%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82%E3%80%80%E5%90%A6%E5%89%87%E7%B1%8C%E5%82%99%E5%B7%A5%E6%A5%AD%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E8%B7%9F%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%90%8C%E8%A1%8C?mtc=20023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2410671%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E3%2580%259144%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2596%2580%25E9%2580%25BE200%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%2590%25A6%25E5%2589%2587%25E7%25B1%258C%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25B7%259F%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%25A1%258C%3Fmtc%3D20023&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hMg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=818c72b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2410671/%E3%80%90%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E3%80%9144%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80%E9%80%BE200%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E4%BF%83%E6%9E%97